==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Decentralize
<hw>De*cen"tral*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to make
less central; to prevent from centralizing; to cause to withdraw from
the center or place of concentration; to divide and distribute (what has
been united or concentrated); -- esp. said of authority, or the
administration of public affairs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deceptible</ent>⟦br⟧
